<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu'n vai A hawm hi,
 A van chutphah chungah;
 A lu-a Lallukhuk, A keng-
 Bula mi thiengte tawh.

[V2]
 Lopina changte tawh,
 Hukdampa kima um;
 I lunguh awi tan a, Dan tak leh;
 Dan tak leh! Dan tak leh!
 I lunguh awi tan a, Dan tak leh.

[V3]
 2. Puon vaka kivan in,
 Simsen loh mipite;
 Guolzawlna Lalmawlh chawi chietin,
 Chawihatna la a sau.

[V4]
 3. Belam No la'n a sau,
 Amau dinga thahsa;
 Belam No tatna thisan ziek,
 Lallukhuk a khuu ui.

[V5]
 4. Lungsiet in, Aw Thagau,
 Nang ei hung panpih in;
 Guolzo Van mithiengte laka
 Ka tel theihna ding un.</lyrics>
<title>ENTHRONED IS JESUS NOW</title>
<hymn_number>154</hymn_number>
</song>